The paper deals with the problem of directional visual sensors, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also proposes an Integer Linear Programming (ILP) formulation, which is a common optimization technique in computer science (cs.DS) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of Integer Quadratic Programming (IQP) and Integer Non-Linear Programming (INLP), which are also common optimization techniques in computer science (cs.IT).
